%p A new post has been submitted and needs your approval before it may be displayed on the website:

%p= link_to 'Approve Post', effective_posts.approve_admin_post_url(@post)

%hr

%h3 Title
%p= @post.title

%h3 Category
%p= @post.category

- if @post.user.present?
  %h3 Submitted by
  %p= @post.user

%h3 Body
%p= @post.body

%hr

%p= link_to 'Approve Post', effective_posts.approve_admin_post_url(@post)
